致重傷者，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或30萬元以下罰金。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MKEM/111%2c%e9%a6%ac%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c63%2c20220930%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MKEM,111,馬交簡,63,20220930,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"馬交簡","JNO":"63","JDATE":"20220930","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}